description:
LARPS DAO is a infinitely generative artwork project which allows its holders to control its treasury.

LARPS are portraits of characters in a splinter civilization emerging from the time loops into the singularity.

They are meant to be enjoyed and collected.  Each portrait has meaningful elements of an emergent narrative and poetic fictive world.

Read more here:
https://zemm.medium.com/larps-a4eddd116c31
